      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
      "body" : "@mindas - the JLS says that there are <a href=\"http://java.sun.com/docs/books/jls/third_edition/html/typesValues.html#4.12.3\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">seven kinds of variables</a>. Method paramaters are fourth on the list."
    }, {
      "owner" : {
        "account_id" : 108117,
        "reputation" : 10699,
        "user_id" : 287138,
        "user_type" : "registered",
        "accept_rate" : 82,
        "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/t2OGY.jpg?s=256",
        "display_name" : "Stefan Haberl",
